cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Digital Libraries (cs.DL) as it deals with bibliometric studies and publication and citation indicators. It could also belong to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses methods for counting and measuring research output. Additionally, it could be classified under Cybernetics (cs.CY) as it deals with the analysis of complex systems. Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses the influence of indicators on the research community. Finally, Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) is a less likely sub-category as it is not directly related to the topic of the paper.
